JavaScript engines zoo
https://github.com/ivankra/javascript-zoo

  * /dist: pre-built JavaScript shell binaries.
    Most can be run directly as a REPL or with a script to run
    as a command-line argument.

  * /zoo: repository checkout with benchmarks and test suites. Examples:
      /zoo/bench/bench.py ./v8
      /zoo/harness/run.py ./quickjs
      /zoo/harness/test262.py ./quickjs  (experimental)

